As I said, ForbiddenOperationException means the username or password is wrong. Keep in mind that username might be an email in case of mojang accounts.

@zuazo I want to remove them because they're hard to work with, have varying quality of results, and don't really catch anything. Sometimes, the test will fail simply because your computer is too slow for the test to complete before the timeout. Take the "Doesn't crash for 20 seconds" test. Is there really any point to that ? It's already more-or-less tested with the other tests...

I just feel like those tests are more of a maintenance burden than an actual help, that's all.

@roblabla 
